'''冰壅'''，或稱'''冰海嘯'''{{r|appledaily}}，是指大量的[[冰|冰]]從湖或海中湧上陸地的現象。<ref name=WLUK>{{cite web |last=Doran |first=Chad |title=Ice shoves cause damage on Lake Winnebago shoreline |url=http://www.fox11online.com/dpp/news/local/fox_cities/ice-shoves-cause-damage-on-lake-winnebago-shoreline |publisher=[[WLUK-TV|WLUK-TV]] |accessdate=2013-01-21 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126005230/http://www.fox11online.com/dpp/news/local/fox_cities/ice-shoves-cause-damage-on-lake-winnebago-shoreline |archivedate=2013-01-26 }}</ref> 他們可能是由[[洋流|洋流]]、強風或者溫度劇烈變化導致的，<ref>{{cite web|title=Glossary for the letter i|url=http://www.crh.noaa.gov/glossary.php?letter=i|publisher=[[National_Oceanic_and_Atmospheric_Administration|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]]|accessdate=2013-01-21|archive-date=2018-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180721052010/http://www.crh.noaa.gov/glossary.php?letter=i|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其高度可達{{convert|12|m|ft}}，雖然一些時候被稱為“冰[[海嘯|海嘯]]”，<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web |author=All Things Considered |url=http://www.npr.org/2013/05/14/183984438/ice-shove-damages-some-manitoba-homes-beyond-repair |title='Ice Shove' Damages Some Manitoba Homes Beyond Repair |publisher=NPR |date=2013-04-24 |accessdate=2013-05-15 |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515194636/http://www.npr.org/2013/05/14/183984438/ice-shove-damages-some-manitoba-homes-beyond-repair |dead-url=no }}</ref> 但其成因更像是某些[[冰山|冰山]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/13/us/ice-tsunamis/index.html |title='Ice tsunamis' sweep into homes |publisher=CNN.com |date= |accessdate=2013-05-15 |archive-date=2019-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227120833/https://www.cnn.com/2013/05/13/us/ice-tsunamis/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 據目擊者描述，這種現象伴隨著巨大的類似火車或者雷聲的轟鳴。<ref name=WLUK /><ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/story/2013/05/13/mb-ochre-beach-ice-wall-manitoba.html |title=Winds whip up worry in Manitoba community hit by ice wall - Manitoba - CBC News |publisher=CBC News (Manitoba) |date=2013-05-13 |accessdate=2013-05-15 |language=en |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515034403/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/story/2013/05/13/mb-ochre-beach-ice-wall-manitoba.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated3">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/story/2013/05/10/mb-ochre-river-beach-ice-wave-homes.html |title=Wall of ice destroys Manitoba homes, cottages |publisher=CBC News (Manitoba) |date=2013-05-10 |accessdate=2013-05-15 |language=en |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515034344/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/story/2013/05/10/mb-ochre-river-beach-ice-wave-homes.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated1"/> 冰壅會摧毀沿岸建築。<ref name=WLUK /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fX3PkXiYO4k|accessdate=2013-05-13|title=Ice Tsunami on Mille Lacs|archive-date=2013-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512084430/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fX3PkXiYO4k&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="autogenerated1"/><ref name="autogenerated2"/><ref name="autogenerated3"/>

